<div class="container marketing">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-4">
      <%= image_tag 'flat.jpg', class: "rounded-circle", width: "140", height: "140"%>
      <h2>Flats</h2>
      <p>In this section you will find an apartment suitable for any of your desires. Here you will find a wide and up-to-date range of apartments, from a small cozy studio to a spacious penthouse. Go to the catalog and choose the apartment of your dreams!</p>
      <%= link_to 'View all flats', flats_catalog_path,  class: "btn btn-secondary" %>
      <% if user_signed_in? %>
        </br><%= link_to 'Add new flat', new_flat_path,  class: "btn btn-secondary mt-2" %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-4">
      <%= image_tag 'country_side_house.jpg', class: "rounded-circle", width: "140", height: "140"%>
      <h2>Country side houses</h2>
      <p>Do you want to live away from the bustle of the city and noisy neighbors? This section is for you. Do you want a house near the forest? Maybe on the shore of a lake or river? Or a well-maintained dacha with a garden and a vegetable garden? Then go to the directory and find the house that you like!</p>
      <%= link_to 'View all country side houses', country_side_houses_catalog_path,  class: "btn btn-secondary" %>
      <% if user_signed_in? %>
        <%= link_to 'Add new country side house', new_country_side_house_path,  class: "btn btn-secondary mt-2" %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-4">
      <%= image_tag 'commercial_premise.jpg', class: "rounded-circle", width: "140", height: "140"%>
      <h2>Commercial premises</h2>
      <p>This directory will help you find any commercial space to implement any of your business ideas. Look here for everything from bars to shopping centers and make all your ambitions come true!</p>
      <%= link_to 'View all commercial premises', commercial_premises_catalog_path,  class: "btn btn-secondary" %>
      <% if user_signed_in? %>
        <%= link_to 'Add new commercial premise', new_commercial_premise_path,  class: "btn btn-secondary mt-2" %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <hr class="featurette-divider mt-5">
  <div class="row featurette mt-5">
    <div class="col-md-7">
      <h2 class="featurette-heading">The light is what guides you home, the warmth is what keeps you there.</h2>
      <p class="lead">Ellie Rodriguez.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-5">
      <%= image_tag 'housee.jpg', width: "500", height: "500"%>
    </div>
  </div>
  <hr class="featurette-divider mt-5">
  <div class="row featurette mt-5">
    <div class="col-md-7 order-md-2">
      <h2 class="featurette-heading">Just an hour away from most major cities, you can always find affordable real estate. You need to find an area that is growing in value, and over time, the property will fall under revaluation. By the time you retire, these three houses will be generating a steady incomeâ€”much more reliable than a mutual fund.</h2>
      <p class="lead">Rich dad, poor dad. <span class="text-muted">Robert Kiyosaki.</span></p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-5 order-md-1">
      <%= image_tag 'minecraft.jpg', width: "500", height: "500"%>
    </div>
  </div>
  <hr class="featurette-divider mt-5">
  <div class="row featurette mt-5">
    <div class="col-md-7">
      <h2 class="featurette-heading">In a cramped apartment, even thoughts are cramped.</h2>
      <p class="lead">Fedor Mikhailovich Dostoevsky. <span class="text-muted">Humiliated and insulted.</span></p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-5">
      <%= image_tag 'little_flat.jpg', width: "500", height: "500"%>
